Valente Rodriguez https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Valente_Rodriguez 0 Valente Rodriguez is an American actor. He is best known for his role as Ernie Cardenas on the sitcom George Lopez. He also starred as Cesar in the TV Land sitcom Happily Divorced. Valente_Rodriguez is an_American_actor . He is_best_known for his_role as Ernie_Cardenas on the_sitcom_George_Lopez .
